desc: A New Type of Cereal - More Protein, Less Carbs and Zero Sugar in Every Serving. Tastes just like your Favourite Cereal Classics. Real Breakfast Joy without all the Regret. Free UK Delivery over £20.

layout.text: WAKE UP TO A NEW TYPE OF CEREAL
Calling those who woke up wishing their breakfast wasn’t so galactically dull. Enjoy cereal again with a revelatory protein-rich, low-carb, and sugar-free breakfast that tastes out of this world.
